text: Jimmy Dzingai (born 21 November 1990) is a Zimbabwean footballer. He plays as a defender for Bangladesh Premier League club Muktijoddha Sangsad. He also plays for the Zimbabwe national team. ==Other websites== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:2019 Africa Cup of Nations players
